         <abstract>
            <p>There exist two distinct works under the title of <foreign xml:lang="gez">Maṣḥafa
                  faws manfasāwi</foreign>, both penitential manuals for confessors having an Arabic
               origin.</p>
            <p>
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4017Mashafa"/> was compiled by <persName ref="PRS7054Michael"/>, while <ref target="#t1"/> was transmitted anonymously.
                  <listBibl type="secondary">
                  <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Kleiner2005EAEFaws"/>
                  </bibl>
               </listBibl>
            </p>
         </abstract>
