                           <citedRange unit="page">216-229</citedRange>
                        </bibl>
                        <!--Arabic-->
                     </listBibl>
                  </desc>
               </div>

               <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Introduction3">
                  <head>
                     <title xml:id="t3" xml:lang="gez">ነገር፡ ዘከመ፡ እፎ፡ ይደሉ፡ ለዐቃቤ፡ ሥራይ፡
                        አእምሮ፡</title>
                     <title xml:id="t3arabic" type="normalized" xml:lang="ar">faṣl fī-mā yaǧibu ʿalā
                        ṭ-ṭabīb maʿrifatihī ʾaʿnī muʿallim al-iʿtirāf</title>
                  </head>
                  <desc> The third chapter contains the translation of the treatise <foreign xml:lang="ar">faṣl fī-mā yaǧibu ʿalā ṭ-ṭabīb maʿrifatihī ʾaʿnī muʿallim
                     al-iʿtirāf</foreign>. This chapter is also attested 
                     preceding or following the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4018Mashafa"/> in manuscripts in which it does not form part of the introduction.<listBibl type="editions">
